---
layout: page.njk
title: City Budget
subtitle: Aberdeen's annual budget documents, financial reports, and transparency resources.
description: City of Aberdeen annual budget documents, financial statements, and public transparency information.
breadcrumb:
  - label: Budget
---

<div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-10">
  <div class="lg:col-span-2 space-y-8">
    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The City of Aberdeen is committed to fiscal transparency. The annual budget is prepared by the City Manager, reviewed by the public, and adopted by the Mayor and City Council. All budget documents are available to residents for review.</p>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Budget Documents</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        {% for doc in [
          { label: "FY2026 Adopted Budget", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/pages/budgets" },
          { label: "Where Does Your Money Go? (FY2026)", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/files/where-does-your-money-go-fy2026-0" },
          { label: "FY2025 Budget", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/pages/budgets" },
          { label: "All Budget Archives", url: "https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/finance/pages/budgets" }
        ] %}
        <a href="{{ doc.url }}" class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:border-gov-blue hover:shadow-sm transition-all duration-200 group">
          <svg aria-hidden="true" class="w-8 h-8 text-red-500 flex-shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M4 4a2 2 0 012-2h4.586A2 2 0 0112 2.586L15.414 6A2 2 0 0116 7.414V16a2 2 0 01-2 2H6a2 2 0 01-2-2V4zm2 6a1 1 0 011-1h6a1 1 0 110 2H7a1 1 0 01-1-1zm1 3a1 1 0 100 2h6a1 1 0 100-2H7z" clip-rule="evenodd"/></svg>
          <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-navy group-hover:text-gov-blue transition-colors duration-200">{{ doc.label }}</span>
        </a>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-navy mb-4">Budget Process</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        {% for step in [
          { n: "1", title: "City Manager Prepares", desc: "The City Manager develops the proposed budget based on departmental needs and City Council priorities." },
          { n: "2", title: "Public Comment Period", desc: "Residents have the opportunity to review and comment on the proposed budget at public sessions." },
          { n: "3", title: "City Council Review", desc: "The Mayor and City Council hold work sessions to review and amend the proposed budget." },
          { n: "4", title: "Adoption", desc: "The City Council formally adopts the annual budget, typically before the start of the fiscal year on July 1." }
        ] %}
        <div class="flex gap-4 bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-gov-blue text-white flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-sm flex-shrink-0">{{ step.n }}</div>
          <div>
            <div class="text-sm font-bold text-navy mb-0.5">{{ step.title }}</div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">{{ step.desc }}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-gov-blue-light rounded-xl p-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-navy mb-2">Weekly Activity Reports</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mb-3">The City Manager publishes weekly reports summarizing city expenditures and operations. A great way to stay informed about how the City is using public resources.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/home/pages/2026-weekly-activity-reports" class="text-sm text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">2026</a>
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/home/pages/2025-weekly-activity-reports" class="text-sm text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">2025</a>
        <a href="https://www.aberdeenmd.gov/home/pages/2024-city-hall-weekly-activity-reports" class="text-sm text-gov-blue font-semibold hover:underline">2024</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <aside>
    <div class="bg-white border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-6 sticky top-24 space-y-5">
      <h2 class="text-base font-bold text-navy pb-3 border-b border-slate-100">Finance Department</h2>
      <dl class="space-y-3 text-sm">
